      • playGame

        public void playGame(Color color)
        This function makes the match play. If the parameter color is BLACK, it's blackPlayer's turn to move, else if the parameter color is WHITE, it's whitePlayer's turn to move. It also gets the match's round number.
        Parameters:
        color: - indicates who has to play
